imdb.plot outline: Sunset Television is a Brooklyn-based comedy group that blurs the line between original content and found footage to create a distinct blend of mysterious, hilarious, and bizarre entertainment. Evolving over the years, their work has taken the form of strange TV shows, undiscovered cult films, and nonsense commercials. They create a unique world where cops become stoners, the dogs are soft and glowing, and Satan loves Chinese food.
imdb.title: Sunset Television
plot: _Sunset Television_ (qv) is a Brooklyn-based comedy group that blurs the line between original content and found footage to create a distinct blend of mysterious, hilarious, and bizarre entertainment. Evolving over the years, their work has taken the form of strange TV shows, undiscovered cult films, and nonsense commercials. They create a unique world where cops become stoners, the dogs are soft and glowing, and Satan loves Chinese food.
